# Hookah Lounge Operations Checklist

This comprehensive checklist covers everything you need to streamline your hookah lounge operations.

## Session Management
- [ ] Set up QR codes for each table
- [ ] Configure session pricing (time-based or flat-rate)
- [ ] Set up automated session timers
- [ ] Configure refill reminders

## Staff Workflow
- [ ] Assign BOH staff roles
- [ ] Assign FOH staff roles
- [ ] Set up staff notifications
- [ ] Configure workflow automation

## Inventory Management
- [ ] Set up flavor inventory tracking
- [ ] Configure low stock alerts
- [ ] Set up automatic reordering

## Customer Experience
- [ ] Enable flavor wheel selection
- [ ] Set up loyalty program
- [ ] Configure special instructions capture
- [ ] Enable guest memory features

## Revenue Optimization
- [ ] Set up dynamic pricing
- [ ] Configure upsell prompts
- [ ] Enable session extension offers
- [ ] Set up referral program

